{
  "meta": {
    "is_partial": true,
    "description": "주문 배송지 변경 모달",
    "editor_label": "$t:user.modal_label.mypage_orders.changeAddressModal"
  },
  "type": "composite",
  "name": "Modal",
  "id": "changeAddressModal",
  "props": {
    "title": "$t:mypage.order_detail.change_shipping_address",
    "size": "md",
    "closeOnBackdropClick": false
  },
  "children": [
    {
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "props": { "className": "space-y-4" },
      "children": [
        {
          "comment": "탭: 저장된 배송지 / 직접 입력 — 회원만. 비회원은 주소록이 없어 탭 없이 직접입력 폼만 노출.",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "if": "{{_global.currentUser?.uuid}}",
          "props": { "className": "flex border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700" },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Button",
              "props": {
                "type": "button",
                "className": "{{(_global.changeAddressMode ?? 'saved') === 'saved' ? 'px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium border-b-2 border-gray-900 dark:border-white text-gray-900 dark:text-white' : 'px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-700 dark:hover:text-gray-300'}}"
              },
              "text": "$t:mypage.order_detail.saved_addresses",
              "actions": [
                {
                  "type": "click",
                  "handler": "setState",
                  "params": { "target": "global", "changeAddressMode": "saved" }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Button",
              "props": {
                "type": "button",
                "className": "{{(_global.changeAddressMode ?? 'saved') === 'manual' ? 'px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium border-b-2 border-gray-900 dark:border-white text-gray-900 dark:text-white' : 'px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-700 dark:hover:text-gray-300'}}"
              },
              "text": "$t:mypage.order_detail.manual_input",
              "actions": [
                {
                  "type": "click",
                  "handler": "setState",
                  "params": { "target": "global", "changeAddressMode": "manual" }
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "comment": "저장된 배송지 목록 — 회원 + saved 탭. 비회원은 주소록이 없어 비노출.",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "if": "{{_global.currentUser?.uuid && (_global.changeAddressMode ?? 'saved') === 'saved'}}",
          "props": { "className": "space-y-2 max-h-80 overflow-y-auto" },
          "children": [
            {
              "comment": "배송지 있을 때",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Div",
              "if": "{{(userAddresses?.data?.addresses?.data ?? []).length > 0}}",
              "props": { "className": "space-y-2" },
              "iteration": { "source": "{{userAddresses?.data?.addresses?.data ?? []}}", "item_var": "addr", "index_var": "addrIdx" },
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Div",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "{{_global.selectedAddressId === addr.id ? 'border-2 border-gray-900 dark:border-white rounded-lg p-3 cursor-pointer bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700' : 'border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700/50 transition-colors'}}"
                  },
                  "actions": [
                    {
                      "type": "click",
                      "handler": "setState",
                      "params": { "target": "global", "selectedAddressId": "{{addr.id}}" }
                    }
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Div",
                      "props": { "className": "flex items-center gap-2 mb-1" },
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "basic",
                          "name": "Span",
                          "props": { "className": "font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-sm" },
                          "text": "{{$localized(addr.name)}}"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "basic",
                          "name": "Span",
                          "if": "{{addr.is_default}}",
                          "props": { "className": "inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-xs bg-gray-900 dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-gray-900 rounded font-medium" },
                          "children": [
                            { "type": "basic", "name": "Icon", "props": { "name": "star", "className": "w-2.5 h-2.5" } },
                            { "type": "basic", "name": "Span", "text": "$t:mypage.addresses.default" }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "P",
                      "props": { "className": "text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" },
                      "text": "{{addr.recipient_name}} | {{addr.recipient_phone}}"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "P",
                      "props": { "className": "text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" },
                      "text": "[{{addr.zipcode}}] {{addr.address}} {{addr.address_detail}}"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "comment": "배송지 없을 때",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Div",
              "if": "{{!(userAddresses?.data?.addresses?.data ?? []).length}}",
              "props": { "className": "text-center py-8" },
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Icon",
                  "props": { "name": "map-pin", "className": "w-10 h-10 mx-auto text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-600 mb-2" }
                },
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "P",
                  "props": { "className": "text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" },
                  "text": "$t:mypage.addresses.empty"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "comment": "직접 입력 폼 — 비회원은 항상 노출(탭 없음), 회원은 manual 탭 선택 시 노출. 모달은 부모 _local 미접근이므로 dataKey 를 _global.editingShippingAddress 로 설정(트리거가 현재 배송지로 채움). 내부 Input 의 name(recipient_name 등 하위 키)이 _global.editingShippingAddress 와 자동 동기화됨. _modal_address.json(_global.editingAddress) 와 동일 패턴. 자동바인딩 Input 에는 수동 value 를 두지 않는다.",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "if": "{{!_global.currentUser?.uuid || (_global.changeAddressMode ?? 'saved') === 'manual'}}",
          "dataKey": "_global.editingShippingAddress",
          "props": { "className": "space-y-3" },
          "children": [
            {
              "comment": "받는 분 + 연락처",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Div",
              "props": { "className": "grid grid-cols-2 gap-3" },
              "responsive": {
                "portable": {
                  "props": { "className": "grid grid-cols-1 gap-3" }
                }
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Div",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Label",
                      "props": { "className": "block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1" },
                      "children": [
                        { "type": "basic", "name": "Span", "text": "$t:mypage.addresses.form.recipient" },
                        { "type": "basic", "name": "Span", "props": { "className": "text-red-500 ml-0.5" }, "text": "*" }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Input",
                      "props": {
                        "type": "text",
                        "name": "recipient_name",
                        "placeholder": "$t:mypage.addresses.form.recipient_placeholder",
                        "required": true,
                        "className": "w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-900 dark:text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gray-900 dark:focus:ring-white focus:border-transparent transition-colors text-sm"
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Div",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Label",
                      "props": { "className": "block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1" },
                      "children": [
                        { "type": "basic", "name": "Span", "text": "$t:mypage.addresses.form.phone" },
                        { "type": "basic", "name": "Span", "props": { "className": "text-red-500 ml-0.5" }, "text": "*" }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Input",
                      "props": {
                        "type": "tel",
                        "name": "recipient_phone",
                        "placeholder": "$t:mypage.addresses.form.phone_placeholder",
                        "required": true,
                        "className": "w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-900 dark:text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gray-900 dark:focus:ring-white focus:border-transparent transition-colors text-sm"
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "comment": "주소 검색",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Div",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Label",
                  "props": { "className": "block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1" },
                  "children": [
                    { "type": "basic", "name": "Span", "text": "$t:mypage.addresses.form.address" },
                    { "type": "basic", "name": "Span", "props": { "className": "text-red-500 ml-0.5" }, "text": "*" }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Div",
                  "props": { "className": "space-y-2" },
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Div",
                      "props": { "className": "flex gap-2" },
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "basic",
                          "name": "Input",
                          "props": {
                            "type": "text",
                            "name": "zipcode",
                            "placeholder": "$t:shop.checkout.zipcode_placeholder",
                            "className": "w-28 px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-sm",
                            "readOnly": true
                          }
                        },
                        {
                          "id": "modal_change_address_search_slot",
                          "type": "extension_point",
                          "name": "address_search_slot",
                          "props": {
                            "readOnlyFields": ["zipcode", "address"]
                          },
                          "callbacks": {
                            "onAddressSelect": {
                              "handler": "setState",
                              "params": {
                                "target": "global",
                                "editingShippingAddress.zipcode": "{{$event.zipcode}}",
                                "editingShippingAddress.address": "{{$event.address}}",
                                "editingShippingAddress.region": "{{$event.region}}",
                                "editingShippingAddress.city": "{{$event.city}}"
                              }
                            }
                          }
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Input",
                      "props": {
                        "type": "text",
                        "name": "address",
                        "placeholder": "$t:shop.checkout.address_placeholder",
                        "className": "w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-sm",
                        "readOnly": true
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "comment": "상세 주소",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Div",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Label",
                  "props": { "className": "block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1" },
                  "text": "$t:mypage.addresses.form.detail_address"
                },
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Input",
                  "props": {
                    "type": "text",
                    "name": "address_detail",
                    "placeholder": "$t:mypage.addresses.form.detail_placeholder",
                    "className": "w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-900 dark:text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gray-900 dark:focus:ring-white focus:border-transparent transition-colors text-sm"
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "comment": "버튼 영역",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "props": { "className": "flex justify-end gap-2 mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700" },
          "responsive": {
            "portable": {
              "props": { "className": "flex gap-2 mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700" }
            }
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Button",
              "props": {
                "type": "button",
                "className": "px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors"
              },
              "responsive": {
                "portable": {
                  "props": {
                    "type": "button",
                    "className": "flex-1 px-4 py-2.5 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors"
                  }
                }
              },
              "text": "$t:common.cancel",
              "actions": [
                { "type": "click", "handler": "closeModal" }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Button",
              "props": {
                "type": "button",
                "className": "flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-gray-900 dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-gray-900 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-gray-800 dark:hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed",
                "disabled": "{{_local.isSubmittingAddress === true}}"
              },
              "responsive": {
                "portable": {
                  "props": {
                    "type": "button",
                    "className": "flex-1 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-4 py-2.5 bg-gray-900 dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-gray-900 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-gray-800 dark:hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed",
                    "disabled": "{{_local.isSubmittingAddress === true}}"
                  }
                }
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Icon",
                  "if": "{{_local.isSubmittingAddress}}",
                  "props": { "name": "spinner", "className": "animate-spin", "size": "sm" }
                },
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Span",
                  "text": "{{_local.isSubmittingAddress ? '$t:common.processing' : '$t:mypage.order_detail.apply_change'}}"
                }
              ],
              "actions": [
                {
                  "comment": "적용 — 회원/비회원 단일 커스텀 핸들러. 핸들러가 _global(changeAddressMode/selectedAddressId/editingShippingAddress/guestOrderToken) 을 읽어 endpoint(user vs guest)+body(address_id vs 직접입력)+토큰 헤더를 분기하고, isSubmittingAddress 처리중 상태·모달 닫기·order 리패치·토스트까지 모두 처리한다 (cancel/confirm-option 과 동일 패턴). confirm 1회는 핸들러 호출 액션에 둔다.",
                  "type": "click",
                  "handler": "sirsoft-ecommerce.changeShippingAddress",
                  "confirm": "$t:mypage.order_detail.confirm_change_address",
                  "params": { "orderId": "{{order.data.id}}" }
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}